{"tid":1824054,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"海洋公園：未來將關閉海洋劇場表演、瘋狂過山車﹑滑浪飛船","createTime":"2020-01-14T07:23:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-16T15:08:16.000Z","uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"9a77272e39abc18cf046c9f2fbcb23b27ea38208","tid":1824054,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T07:23:45.000Z","msg":"海洋公園計劃以過百億元公帑推行新發展計劃，將劃分為7個主題區，將增設20個景點至超過100個，但現有12個設施會關閉，包括瘋狂過山車﹑滑浪飛船和兩個兒童王國內的遊樂設施，及取消海洋劇場演出。<br />\n<br />\n海洋公園主席孔令成說，明白市民重視集體回憶，但園內設施老化，維修成本高昂，園方要留意經營成本，強調新計劃下的設施會更吸引，希望公園能成為「真正香港人的公園」。<br />\n<br />\n新計劃全面落成後首年度每年入場人次預計750萬，被問到以過百億元翻新，才大致回復至2012/13年入場人次水平，是否物有所值，海洋公園行政總裁李繩宗回應，並非以人次推動公園收入，相信新計劃針對高消費力自由行旅客，能增加收入，目前未有打算調整票價。<br />\n<br />\n對於園方關閉標誌性設施海洋劇場，李繩宗強調公園是重要的保育基地，園方對飼養動物的透明度高，一直都有定時公布相關資料，生態保育及動物飼養仍擔當重要的角色。<br />\n<br />\n政府建議給予海洋公園106億4千萬元一次過資助，支持全新發展計劃，同時建議兩筆政府貸款豁免利息，並推遲還款期8年，令庫房收入減少24億6千萬元 。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1502565-20200113.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1502565-20200113.htm&d=RrW1hT%2ByM3GEQeJ1bMSeriUaeeTarj8%2BpjPG%2B7PQGFg%3D&h=4dd4ddab\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1502565-20200113.htm&h=646d7510\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1502565-20200113.htm</a>"},{"pid":"dc854355105f179a351c009df4f79fd9d48b69c5","tid":1824054,"uid":242537,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T07:28:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://media.whatscap.com/c74/c5e/c74c5ee398220cd735efae1df8c2ab53af1f8b87_n.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.whatscap.com%2Fc74%2Fc5e%2Fc74c5ee398220cd735efae1df8c2ab53af1f8b87_n.jpg&h=779b0b28&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://media.whatscap.com/0d5/7fc/0d57fcbbd553773c51b34b8ec3bef68bed5cfb49_n.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.whatscap.com%2F0d5%2F7fc%2F0d57fcbbd553773c51b34b8ec3bef68bed5cfb49_n.jpg&h=c54a87c3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"33801511f89a30362d1edb4d02ca6bb9692201ea","tid":1824054,"uid":304321,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T07:29:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LDA7tL5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLDA7tL5.jpg&h=e37804d1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"74eeff971262cdf31452348f0bfbf1d85b9e364b","tid":1824054,"uid":201604,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T07:29:49.000Z","msg":"冇晒中國人先黎話希望公園能成為「真正香港人的公園」。"},{"pid":"7d8bba1d992357e9a28d2fcde97e8b6963bcbc4c","tid":1824054,"uid":63154,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T07:29:57.000Z","msg":"未來將關閉海洋公園<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d879ac94e9836724eb9ad80110ef88f532ee0d1","tid":1824054,"uid":105219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T07:30:43.000Z","msg":"咁啲海豚咪失業？"},{"pid":"4f349527a56079648761707d95fd1dae5e6f202b","tid":1824054,"uid":149978,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9d879ac94e9836724eb9ad80110ef88f532ee0d1","tid":1824054,"uid":105219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T07:30:43.000Z","msg":"咁啲海豚咪失業？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T07:33:56.000Z","msg":"樂園裡的海洋哺乳類動物，包括海豚、海獅等，將會遷移至位於探險家<strong>海岸的新展館</strong>。<br />\n<br />\n新展館將會為海洋動物提供一個度身訂造、 適合多品種共同棲息的環境，而訪客更可同時欣賞牠們在水底的美妙姿態。<br />\n<br />\n而原有的海洋劇場將會改建成為新的多用途表演場館。<br />\n<br />\n即係無左海豚表演，但有得睇海豚。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.weekendhk.com/1007775/lifestyle/weekend-leisure/%e6%b5%b7%e6%b4%8b%e5%85%ac%e5%9c%92-%e6%94%b9%e5%bb%ba-%e6%99%af%e9%bb%9e-%e4%b8%bb%e9%a1%8c%e5%8d%80-%e9%a6%99%e6%b8%af%e5%a5%bd%e5%8e%bb%e8%99%95/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.weekendhk.com%2F1007775%2Flifestyle%2Fweekend-leisure%2F%25e6%25b5%25b7%25e6%25b4%258b%25e5%2585%25ac%25e5%259c%2592-%25e6%2594%25b9%25e5%25bb%25ba-%25e6%2599%25af%25e9%25bb%259e-%25e4%25b8%25bb%25e9%25a1%258c%25e5%258d%2580-%25e9%25a6%2599%25e6%25b8%25af%25e5%25a5%25bd%25e5%258e%25bb%25e8%2599%2595%2F&d=RrW1hT%2ByM3GEQeJ1bMSeriUaeeTarj8%2BpjPG%2B7PQGFg%3D&h=e7f465d1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.weekendhk.com/1007775/lifestyle/weekend-leisure/%e6%b5%b7%e6%b4%8b%e5%85%ac%e5%9c%92-%e6%94%b9%e5%bb%ba-%e6%99%af%e9%bb%9e-%e4%b8%bb%e9%a1%8c%e5%8d%80-%e9%a6%99%e6%b8%af%e5%a5%bd%e5%8e%bb%e8%99%95/</a>"},{"pid":"7a37ef5ac5b44c6680ecf41e954001d5835602a1","tid":1824054,"uid":189528,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T07:34:12.000Z","msg":"滑浪飛船收左，不如汁7左佢"},{"pid":"892dd2e337cfc60b9761c404fcf3e475e87ab4c7","tid":1824054,"uid":4964,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"74eeff971262cdf31452348f0bfbf1d85b9e364b","tid":1824054,"uid":201604,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T07:29:49.000Z","msg":"冇晒中國人先黎話希望公園能成為「真正香港人的公園」。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T07:34:52.000Z","msg":"就好似當年亞視話有一半市場喺中國，迫鳩全香港用中國高清制式，結果中國人根本就唔撚睇你，執柒埋"},{"pid":"ead1083d4d94ca42365a166129b17a25b17428aa","tid":1824054,"uid":254410,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T07:42:31.000Z","msg":"政府建議給予海洋公園106億4千萬元<span style=\"color: red;\">一次過資助</span>，支持全新發展計劃，同時建議兩筆政府貸款豁免利息，並推遲還款期8年，令庫房收入減少24億6千萬元 。<br />\n<br />\n真係一次!? 到時啲工程樣樣開曬, 做到一半已經洗曬100億 政府咪又係要俾<br />\n個陣又會話唔想浪費洗左既100億要注資多50億<br />\n最仆街係管理不善既人一日唔換俾幾多錢都係冇用<br />\n只係識攞啲最低層既人既刀"},{"pid":"d19a328895ab19835a5f0487674f9adcb5323cc6","tid":1824054,"uid":288523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T08:03:09.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"854f0f191faee903452e89ac6d25b9a02d79bce1","tid":1824054,"uid":973,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T08:16:53.000Z","msg":"認真海豚表演真係核心黎<br />\n以前去睇殺人鯨都係去海洋公園動力黎<br />\n無左真係好可惜<br />\n<br />\n仲有個過山車算係少數比較刺激機動游戲<br />\n無左真係得返越礦飛車<br />\n完全無料到<img s